INSERT INTO
    ais_vms_area_positions AS a (
        latitude,
        longitude,
        call_sign,
        "timestamp",
        position_type_id,
        mmsi
    )
SELECT
    u.latitude,
    u.longitude,
    av.call_sign,
    u."timestamp",
    u.position_type_id,
    u.mmsi
FROM
    UNNEST(
        $1::DOUBLE PRECISION[],
        $2::DOUBLE PRECISION[],
        $3::TIMESTAMPTZ[],
        $4::INT[],
        $5::INT[]
    ) u (
        latitude,
        longitude,
        "timestamp",
        position_type_id,
        mmsi
    )
    INNER JOIN ais_vessels av ON av.mmsi = u.mmsi
    LEFT JOIN fiskeridir_ais_vessel_mapping_whitelist f ON av.call_sign = f.call_sign
WHERE
    (
        av.call_sign IS NULL
        OR f.fiskeridir_vessel_id IS NOT NULL
    )
ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING
RETURNING
    a.latitude,
    a.longitude,
    a."timestamp",
    a.mmsi,
    a.call_sign
